                            <picture>
                                <source media="(min-width:1024px)" srcset="/media/cztcusb3/maud-langaskens400x400-uprofile-thumb-homepage.png?rxy=0.5%2c0.3085226728702184&amp;width=509&amp;height=493&amp;v=1db0045e7b788b0&amp;format=webp">
                                <img src="/media/cztcusb3/maud-langaskens400x400-uprofile-thumb-homepage.png?rxy=0.5%2c0.3085226728702184&amp;width=388&amp;height=354&amp;v=1db0045e7b788b0&amp;format=webp" alt="Webdeveloper working at desk" loading="lazy">
                            </picture>
                            <p>Maud Langaskens</p>
                            <span>Read Maud's uProfile'</span>
